2012-01-01|2012-12-30.description: The ancient city of Bam is burning and Buran's nephew is missing. Meanwhile in Paris, The 99's newest member Sami the Listener is also missing. Dr. Ramzi sends out two teams to locate the missing teens. The team that is sent to Bam discovers a new gem-bearer with a fiery ability, the other team discovers...
2012-01-01|2012-12-30.name: Firefight

2012-01-01|2012-12-30.description: In the aftermath of the zombie invasion and major heartbreaks, Gwen is hiding out in her crypt until the heat dies down. But Galatea and Dr. Coffee are determined to give the town of Eugene more to worry about – and the only one standing in the way of their evil scheme is Amon, the dashing, deadly mummy.
2012-01-01|2012-12-30.name: Mix It Up, Part 1

2012-01-01|2012-12-30.description: RUN THE MISSION. DON'T GET SEEN. SAVE THE WORLD.Something is dangerously awry in the Office Of National Emergency (O*N*E)...
2012-01-01|2012-12-30.name: Final Level

2012-01-01|2012-12-30.description: In a misguided attempt to save the Earth, Batman launches a chemical attack on an alien race. Will Hal Jordan and the Green Lantern Corps arrive in time to stop the genocide?
2012-01-01|2012-12-30.name: Shades

2012-01-01|2012-12-30.description:
The final brutal confrontation between the Punisher and the Kingpin!

Only one of these men is going to walk away alive.

Final chapter of the HOMELESS arc.
2012-01-01|2012-12-30.name: Homeless, Conclusion

2012-01-01|2012-12-30.description: This stand alone story is jam packed with malevolent Mixed Martial Arts mayhem, as Green Hornet and Kato enter a cage match with the baddest men in Century City! Britt Reid and Mulan have decided to enjoy a nice, street clothes night out at the fights. When an old college buddy of Britt's is seriously injured in the octagon, our heroes join the fray. Now, Green Hornet and Kato have to stay alive in a bloody cage match to the death against the very fighters they bought tickets to see.
The distant future Earth is inhabited by alien settlers that feed off of the ape-men mankind has devolved into. John Prophet awakes from cryosleep on a mission to restart the human empire.
2012-01-01|2012-12-30.name: Prophet

2012-01-01|2012-12-30.description: STORM IS NOW AN AVENGER!HOW CAN THE AVENGERS BATTLE THE COMBINED FORCES OF HYDRA, AIM, THE HAND, AND H.A.M.M.E.R. UNDER THE LEADERSHIP OF NORMAN OSBORN?
2012-01-01|2012-12-30.name: Mess with the Goddess,get the Storm!

2012-01-01|2012-12-30.description:
Wolverine and AOA Nightcrawler face a strange and deadly new foe in Otherworld

Fantomex’s sentence is carried out and he is injected with an anti-reality serum…

Psylocke becomes Lady Briton!

Deadpool is decapitated!
2012-01-01|2012-12-30.name: Otherworld, Chapter Two

2012-01-01|2012-12-30.description: Daken sets out to get his revenge on the man he hates most in the world: Wolverine. And if the whole Marvel Universe has to bleed for that to happen then that's just fine.
2012-01-01|2012-12-30.name: Lost Weekend, Pt. 1

2012-01-01|2012-12-30.description: It's the big showdown between the Kilgore brothers and the swarming hordes of the Second Church in the heart of Radical City! With the help of an enigmatic new ally, Haunt cuts loose on his enemies... but will it be enough to ensure his escape?
2012-01-01|2012-12-30.name: The Glorious Orgy

2012-01-01|2012-12-30.description:
The New Avengers battle the Dark Avengers. One Avenger leaves the team in defeat. RAGNAROK!

Perrin is warned by the wolves about the approach of unfriendly visitors to the stedding - the Children of the Light, whose arrival comes with a deadly cost... to both sides. Can Perrin and Egwene avoid capture, or will they be at the mercy of the Children? Join us for Children of Shadow, the next chapter in the thrilling adaptation of Robert Jordan's fantasy epic The Wheel of Time: The Eye of the World!

volume.name: Robert Jordan's Wheel of Time: The Eye of the World

2012-01-01|2012-12-30.description: A new chapter in the Gantz saga brings with it a new level of action and mayhem! The alien-hunting Gantz warriors are transported to their new mission, leaving behind their fallen comrades, Kurono and Izumi. Given no time to mourn, they find themselves in a completely unfamiliar location, well beyond the confines of Tokyo in the Dotombori district of Osaka. Even more surprising is an encounter with another group in Gantz suits. Are the members of this unknown team allies . . . or deadly new foes?
2012-01-01|2012-12-30.name: Volume 21

2012-01-01|2012-12-30.description: Freak. Reject. Loner. Sideshow attraction. Killer. Here is the tragic tale of Arkham City's most fearsome menace, the sewer-dwelling Killer Croc. Find out where he came from and how he ended up where he is today. It's an origin that's as heartbreaking as it is terrifying.
2012-01-01|2012-12-30.name: Crocodile Tears (Part 2)

2012-01-01|2012-12-30.description: Series Finale! X-23'S Globehopping Journey Comes To A Close. After All This Time Spent Choosing Who She Will Be, Will She Permanently Choose A Team As Well?
2012-01-01|2012-12-30.name: Girls Night Out, Part 2

2012-01-01|2012-12-30.description: It’s do or die for the Shohoku High School Basketball Team! If they want a spot in the Nationals, they need to win this game. As the second half winds down, Shohoku hangs on to a one-point lead over Ryonan despite Mitsui’s collapse. Ryonan keeps the pressure on with their best players, Uozumi, Fukuda and Sendoh, giving it all they’ve got. Sakuragi steps up defensively, and now he’s Shohoku’s last hope of staying alive in the tournament, but is he up to the challenge?
2012-01-01|2012-12-30.name: Vol. 21

2012-01-01|2012-12-30.description: Using the power of the Sixth Gun, Becky Montcrief invades the sanctum of the Knights of Solomon in order to rescue Drake Sinclair! Becky's enemies have often seen her as the helpless damsel in distress - but no more! Once she's finished with them, the Knights will know without a doubt that she is the deserving wielder of the deadliest weapon ever created!
2012-01-01|2012-12-30.name: A Town Called Penance, Part Four

2012-01-01|2012-12-30.description: With Magic School's doors no longer open, Knox Academy is one of the few places on Earth that can provide a safe haven for those in need. Piper, Phoebe, and Paige must team with the staff to protect themselves and their friends from the government's modern day witch hunt that has deemed anyone like them to be the enemy.
2012-01-01|2012-12-30.name: Reversal of Misfortune

2012-01-01|2012-12-30.description: Scooby-Doo and the rest of the gang have another exciting mystery to solve! Can the gang get to the bottom of the haunted stadium in time for kickoff?
2012-01-01|2012-12-30.name: The Case of the Haunted Huddle; Gridiron Ghoul; The Dragon in the Bathroom

2012-01-01|2012-12-30.description: There once was a boy who imagined the end of the world. It was just a child’s game… but not anymore! The Friend is carrying out his plan for the extermination of the human race—all according to his predictions. And the man who survived Bloody New Year’s Eve is heading toward Tokyo. The boys are coming back together one by one. The time is come. This is the countdown to the final battle.
2012-01-01|2012-12-30.name: Vol. 21

2012-01-01|2012-12-30.description:
Toxin vs. Venom! Flash Thompson’s Last Stand! The Crime-Master Triumphant! – It’s the Savage Six Finale the comics world will be talking about!

CRIME MASTER’S IDENTITY IS REVEALED – and Flash Thompson and Betty Brant’s lives will never be the same!
2012-01-01|2012-12-30.name: Savage Six, Part 4: Best Laid Plans...

2012-01-01|2012-12-30.description: After the startling events of last issue, Vampirella's ready to put everything on the line in an attempt to save one soul and destroy another. Heroes and villains alike are playing toward their own endgame, and the cards are turning with a deadly quickness. We're not kidding when we say that BIG changes are coming, and it all starts here with Part 1 of INQUISITION!
2012-01-01|2012-12-30.name: Vampirella: Inquisition, Part 1 - A Faith-Based Initiative

2012-01-01|2012-12-30.description: In a move that surprises everyone, Black Bolt and the Inhumans return to Earth. What does this mean for Marvel's first family?
2012-01-01|2012-12-30.name: Ronance

2012-01-01|2012-12-30.description:
Always somebody to run from.

The Morning Glory Academy spends a lot of time trying to keep it's students from running away - which isn't an easy task, given that every student there is gifted. Into this environment arrive six new students - eager to begin class at such a prestigious school. But, they soon learn that the school is a front for something sinister.
2012-01-01|2012-12-30.name: One

But Shang is Carter's greatest enemy, and he's not about to hand her over! Mars's greatest hero is in for the wildest ride of his career, and it all starts in Warlord of Mars #21 - The Temple of the Sun!

2012-01-01|2012-12-30.description:
"PHANTOMS OF THE HEART", CONCLUSION

Dr. Rachel Harrison has come to learn the truth of her family heirloom - it is the Artifact known as the Heartstone. What she didn't know is that each Artifact bearer has a destiny and hers lies in the small New England hometown she tried to leave behind. The origin of the Top Cow Universe's newest bearer by RON MARZ (MAGDALENA, SHINKU) and STJEPAN SEJIC (ANGELUS) comes to a chilling conclusion.
2012-01-01|2012-12-30.name: Phantoms of the Heart, Part 3

2012-01-01|2012-12-30.description:
A PARALLEL WORLD

Natsu and the gang journey to Edolas, a parallel world in the sky, in search of their vanished guild. Instead they stumble upon the parallel version of Fairy Tail and find their guild mates all have completely different personalities, as well as a long lost member of the original guild.

The War against Surtur crushes Thor – literally!

Hela and Loki make their move!

Can the All-Mother save the Nine Realms?

Aliens have arrived on Earth-16!

Superboy and five Justice Leaguers have been abducted!

Metropolis is in danger!

Enter: BRAINIAC!

2012-01-01|2012-12-30.name: Detective Part 9

2012-01-01|2012-12-30.description: 'Tis the season to be jolly, that is unless Mr. Weatherbee has anything to say about it! After a ban on holiday decorations is enforced at Riverdale High, the school halls just aren't very festive. Archie and the gang intend to do something about it, but without breaking any of the school rules in "Decoration Daze!"

A battle begins between rebel Claymore warriors and the Organization that created them. When the team of seven notorious rebel fighters is joined by an army of newly minted soldiers loyal to rebel leader Miria, it seems their victory is a foregone conclusion. A NEW INVESTIGATION FOR LEO LODEN'S 20TH YEAR !

A seminar day on the Frioul archipelago brings together the executives of a pharmaceutical company...

The big boss is poisoned and dies during the cocktail party...

That is the perfect investigation for Leo, the perpetrator has to be on the island and it is not the ghost of the Count of Monte Cristo! But appearances might be deceiving...
